Dr. Richard Batista says that eight years ago, he had gifted his wife Dawnell his kidney, to save her life.
According to AFP news agency, it is Dr. Batista's statement that his wife has repayed him for his gift by cheating him and having relations with another man, and now she wants divorce.
Dr. Batista said, during an interview to a local newspaper, Daily News, that her love affair has put a hole in my heart that still exists.
According to Dr. Richard Batista's lawyer, though Dr. Batista is demanding his kidney back, but he actually wants a monetary compensation for the kidney.
He will give his stand about his wife in front of a judge within the next few days.
140 year old, 9 kilo weighing lobster free
'George the Giant Lobster' was captured from the sea two weeks ago.
The Seafood company of the city had purchased it for a hundred Dollars.
And instantly started using the lobster photos for his publicity.
Although, "PETA" a group working for animal rights demanded to release the lobster. As a result of which it will be released in the Sea.
George was caught in Canada from the sea after which he spent 10 days in the city crab and seafood company tank.
The age of lobster can be told by its weight.
Restaurant's manager Keith Walanty says that their purpose was not to hurt the lobster at all. And to keep him in the tank was to provide entertainment to the customers.
Engrid Newkurk from the animal rights group PETA says that restaurant's decision is worth praise and an example for those who want to keep these precious animals in the tank or want to eat them by boiling them alive.
